extendedInfo.description: Did You Put the Cat to Bed?Helen  W. MallonGenre: Literary FictionWord Count:  5,260 Length: Short StorySo Izzy got knocked up.  Not by one of the art school bad boys, but by white-bread Harris, her neighbor. Her churchgoing pillar of a dad reminded Izzy that she "can do anything she puts her mind to,"  the moral heft of this single option given momentum by her father's imminent death from cancer.
